"      -e 's/GROUP=\"sgx\", //' rules.d/50-udev-default.rules.in</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:51
msgid "Prepare systemd for compilation:"
msgstr "Prepare systemd para compilação:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:53
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">mkdir -p build\n"
"cd       build\n"
"\n"
"meson setup \\\n"
"      --prefix=/usr                 \\\n"
"      --buildtype=release           \\\n"
"      -Ddefault-dnssec=no           \\\n"
"      -Dfirstboot=false             \\\n"
"      -Dinstall-tests=false         \\\n"
"      -Dldconfig=false              \\\n"
"      -Dsysusers=false              \\\n"
"      -Drpmmacrosdir=no             \\\n"
"      -Dhomed=false                 \\\n"
"      -Duserdb=false                \\\n"
"      -Dman=false                   \\\n"
"      -Dmode=release                \\\n"
"      -Dpamconfdir=no               \\\n"
"      -Ddev-kvm-mode=0660           \\\n"
"      -Ddocdir=/usr/share/doc/systemd-&systemd-version; \\\n"
"      ..</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">mkdir -p build\n"
"cd      build\n"
"\n"
"meson setup \\\n"
"      --prefix=/usr                 \\\n"
"      --buildtype=release           \\\n"
"      -Ddefault-dnssec=no           \\\n"
"      -Dfirstboot=false             \\\n"
"      -Dinstall-tests=false         \\\n"
"      -Dldconfig=false              \\\n"
"      -Dsysusers=false              \\\n"
"      -Drpmmacrosdir=no             \\\n"
"      -Dhomed=false                 \\\n"
"      -Duserdb=false                \\\n"
"      -Dman=false                   \\\n"
"      -Dmode=release                \\\n"
"      -Dpamconfdir=no               \\\n"
"      -Ddev-kvm-mode=0660           \\\n"
"      -Ddocdir=/usr/share/doc/systemd-&systemd-version; \\\n"
"      ..</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:75
msgid "The meaning of the meson options:"
msgstr "O significado das opções \"meson\":"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:78
msgid "<parameter>--buildtype=release</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>--buildtype=release</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:80
msgid ""
"This switch overrides the default buildtype (<quote>debug</quote>), which "
"produces unoptimized binaries."
msgstr ""
"Essa chave substitui o tipo de construção padrão (<quote>debug</quote>), que "
"produz binários não otimizados."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:87
msgid "<parameter>-Ddefault-dnssec=no</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Ddefault-dnssec=no</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:89
msgid "This switch turns off the experimental DNSSEC support."
msgstr "Essa chave desliga o suporte experimental a DNSSEC."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:94
msgid "<parameter>-Dfirstboot=false</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Dfirstboot=false</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:96
msgid ""
"This switch prevents installation of systemd services responsible for "
"setting up the system for the first time. These are not useful in LFS, "
"because everything is done manually."
msgstr ""
"Essa chave impede a instalação de serviços do systemd responsáveis por "
"configurar o sistema pela primeira vez. Eles não são úteis no LFS, pois tudo "
"é feito manualmente."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:104
msgid "<parameter>-Dinstall-tests=false</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Dinstall-tests=false</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:106
msgid "This switch prevents installation of the compiled tests."
msgstr "Essa chave impede a instalação dos testes compilados."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:111
msgid "<parameter>-Dldconfig=false</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Dldconfig=false</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:113
msgid ""
"This switch prevents installation of a systemd unit that runs "
"<command>ldconfig</command> at boot; this is not useful for source "
"distributions such as LFS, and makes the boot time longer. Remove this "
"option to enable running <command>ldconfig</command> at boot."
msgstr ""
"Essa chave impede a instalação de uma unidade do systemd que executa "
"<command>ldconfig</command> ao inicializar; isso não é útil para "
"distribuições de fonte, tais como o LFS, e torna o tempo de inicialização "
"mais longo. Remova essa opção para habilitar a execução de "
"<command>ldconfig</command> ao inicializar."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:121
msgid "<parameter>-Dsysusers=false</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Dsysusers=false</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:123
msgid ""
"This switch prevents installation of systemd services responsible for "
"setting up the <filename>/etc/group</filename> and <filename>/etc/passwd</"
"filename> files. Both files were created in the previous chapter. This "
"daemon is not useful on an LFS system since user accounts are manually "
"created."
msgstr ""
"Essa chave impede a instalação de serviços do systemd responsáveis por "
"configurar os arquivos <filename>/etc/group</filename> e <filename>/etc/"
"passwd</filename>. Ambos os arquivos foram criados no capítulo anterior. "
"Esse processo de segundo plano não é útil em um sistema LFS dado que contas "
"de usuário(a) são criadas manualmente."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:133
msgid "<parameter>-Drpmmacrosdir=no</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Drpmmacrosdir=no</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:135
msgid ""
"This switch disables installation of RPM Macros for use with systemd, "
"because LFS does not support RPM."
msgstr ""
"Essa chave desabilita a instalação das Macros RPM para uso com o systemd, "
"pois o LFS não suporta RPM."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:141
msgid "<parameter>-D{userdb,homed}=false</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-D{userdb,homed}=false</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:143
msgid ""
"Remove two daemons with dependencies that do not fit within the scope of LFS."
msgstr ""
"Remova dois processos de segundo plano com dependências que não se encaixam "
"no escopo do LFS."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:149
msgid "<parameter>-Dman=false</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Dman=false</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:151
msgid ""
"Prevent the generation of man pages to avoid extra dependencies.  We will "
"install pre-generated man pages for systemd from a tarball."
msgstr ""
"Impeça a geração de páginas de manual para evitar dependências extras. Nós "
"instalaremos páginas de manual pré-geradas para o systemd a partir de um "
"tarball."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:158
msgid "<parameter>-Dmode=release</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Dmode=release</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:160
msgid "Disable some features considered experimental by upstream."
msgstr ""
"Desabilite alguns recursos considerados experimentais pelo(a) "
"desenvolvedor(a)."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:166
msgid "<parameter>-Dpamconfdir=no</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Dpamconfdir=no</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:168
msgid ""
"Prevent the installation of a PAM configuration file not functional on LFS."
msgstr ""
"Evita a instalação de um arquivo de configuração do PAM não funcional no LFS."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:174
msgid "<parameter>-Ddev-kvm-mode=0660</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>-Ddev-kvm-mode=0660</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:176
msgid ""
"The default udev rule would allow all users to access <filename "
"class='devicefile'>/dev/kvm</filename>.  The editors consider it dangerous.  "
"This option overrides it."
msgstr ""
"A regra padrão do \"udev\" permitiria que todos(as) os(as) usuários(as) "
"acessassem <filename class='devicefile'>/dev/kvm</filename>. Os(As) "
"editores(as) a consideram perigosa. Essa opção a substitui."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:183
msgid "Compile the package:"
msgstr "Compile o pacote:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:185
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"make\">ninja</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"make\">ninja</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:187
msgid "Install the package:"
msgstr "Instale o pacote:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:189
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"install\">ninja install</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"install\">ninja install</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:191
msgid "Install the man pages:"
msgstr "Instale as páginas de manual:"

#.  Please make sure systemd man pages tarball has a common leading
#.          component in the path.  
#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:195
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">tar -xf ../../systemd-man-pages-&systemd-version;.tar.xz \\\n"
"    --no-same-owner --strip-components=1   \\\n"
"    -C /usr/share/man</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"install\">tar -xf ../../systemd-man-pages-&systemd-"
"version;.tar.xz \\\n"
"    --no-same-owner --strip-components=1  \\\n"
"    -C /usr/share/man</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:199
msgid ""
"Create the <filename>/etc/machine-id</filename> file needed by "
"<command>systemd-journald</command>:"
msgstr ""
"Crie o arquivo <filename>/etc/machine-id</filename> necessitado pelo "
"<command>systemd-journald</command>:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:202
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"adjust\">systemd-machine-id-setup</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"adjust\">systemd-machine-id-setup</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:204
msgid "Set up the basic target structure:"
msgstr "Configure a estrutura básica alvo:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:206
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"adjust\">systemctl preset-all</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"adjust\">systemctl preset-all</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:208
msgid ""
"Disable two services for upgrading binary distros.  They are useless for a "
"basic Linux system built from source, and each one will report an error if "
"it's enabled but not configured:"
msgstr ""
"Desabilite dois serviços para atualizar distribuições de binário. Eles são "
"inúteis para um sistema básico Linux construído a partir do fonte e cada um "
"informará um erro se estiver habilitado, mas não configurado:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/systemd.xml:212
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput remap=\"adjust\">systemctl disable systemd-sysupdate{,-reboot}</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput remap=\"adjust\">systemctl disable systemd-sysupdate{,-reboot}</userinput>"

